{"problem":{"stackLimit":128,"modifiedUser":"root","auth":1,"isRemote":false,"description":"<p>脱氧核糖核酸(DNA)由两条互补的碱基链以双螺旋的方式结合而成。而构成DNA的碱基共有4种，分别为腺瞟呤(A)、鸟嘌呤(G)、胸腺嘧啶(T)和胞嘧啶(C)。我们知道，在两条互补碱基链的对应位置上，腺瞟呤总是和胸腺嘧啶配对，鸟嘌呤总是和胞嘧啶配对。你的任务就是根据一条单链上的碱基序列，给出对应的互补链上的碱基序列。<p>","removeEndBlank":true,"uploadCase":true,"source":"","remote":false,"title":"配对碱基链 ","type":0,"difficulty":1,"output":"<p>一个只含有大写字母A、T、G、C的字符串，为与输入的碱基链互补的碱基链。<p>","timeLimit":1000,"input":"<p>一个字符串，表示一条碱基链。这个字符串只含有大写字母A、T、G、C，分别表示腺瞟呤、胸腺嘧啶、鸟嘌呤和胞嘧啶。字符串长度不超过255。<p>","examples":"<input>ATATGGATGGTGTTTGGCTCTG\n</input><output>TATACCTACCACAAACCGAGAC\n</output>","ioScore":10000,"codeShare":false,"hint":"","isRemoveEndBlank":true,"openCaseResult":true,"memoryLimit":256,"problemId":"T1135","isUploadCase":true},"languages":["C","C With O2","C++","C++ With O2","Java","Python3","Python2","Golang","C#"],"codeTemplates":[],"isSpj":false,"samples":[{"output":"1.out","input":"1.in","score":100},{"output":"2.out","input":"2.in","score":100},{"output":"3.out","input":"3.in","score":100},{"output":"4.out","input":"4.in","score":100},{"output":"5.out","input":"5.in","score":100},{"output":"6.out","input":"6.in","score":100},{"output":"7.out","input":"7.in","score":100},{"output":"8.out","input":"8.in","score":100},{"output":"9.out","input":"9.in","score":100},{"output":"10.out","input":"10.in","score":100}],"tags":["一本通在线评测"]}